{"products":[{"id":10329962414427,"title":"Euphorbia ingens - Cowboy Cactus - 120-140cm (Semi Mature)","handle":"euphorbia-ingens-cowboy-cactus-120-140cm","body_html":"\u003cp\u003eThe \"\u003cstrong\u003eEuphorbia ingens\u003c\/strong\u003e\", \"\u003cstrong\u003eEuphorbia Eritrea Candelabrum\u003c\/strong\u003e\" or \u003cstrong\u003e\"Cowboy Cactus\"\u003c\/strong\u003e is a striking indoor plant known for its tall sculptural stems and bold architectural shape. This semi mature variety creates an impressive statement in any space and is perfect for bright living rooms, offices or modern interiors.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"621\" data-end=\"964\"\u003eAlthough often called a cactus, Euphorbia ingens is technically a succulent plant that closely resembles a cactus. It grows upright with thick segmented stems that branch out over time, creating a dramatic candelabra style form. The plant can vary in colour from deep green to bluish green and may develop subtle reddish tones along the edges.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"966\" data-end=\"1242\"\u003eEach Cowboy Cactus is completely unique in shape, which makes these plants especially interesting for collectors and plant lovers looking for a distinctive feature plant. Like most succulents, it requires minimal care and thrives in bright conditions with occasional watering.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1244\" data-end=\"1397\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNotes:\u003c\/strong\u003e All large plants come with their plastic nursery pot only and there is no need to re-pot for four or five years. Ceramic pots are sold separately.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1399\" data-end=\"1514\"\u003eAll cacti are individual specimens and the shape of the plant and number of arms may differ from the picture shown.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePlease note there is a 2-3 week lead time on large cacti.\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2026-02-09T16:24:30+00:00","created_at":"2026-02-09T16:21:52+00:00","updated_at":"2026-05-12T21:45:45+01:00","vendor":"Plant Store","product_type":"Cacti\/Succulents","tags":["All Products","Easy Care","most popular"],"variants":[{"id":52218801684827,"title":"Default Title","option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":null,"requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":true,"price":"115.00","grams":0,"compare_at_price":"145.00","position":1,"product_id":10329962414427,"created_at":"2026-02-09T16:21:52+00:00","updated_at":"2026-05-12T21:45:45+01:00"}],"images":[{"id":70150915457371,"created_at":"2026-02-09T16:22:36+00:00","position":1,"updated_at":"2026-02-09T16:22:39+00:00","product_id":10329962414427,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0551\/6489\/files\/Euphorbia140cm.png?v=1770654159","width":600,"height":800}],"options":[{"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}]},{"id":1559199547504,"title":"Amora Plant Container - Metal Blue","handle":"copy-of-ceramic-plant-containers-imperial-blue","body_html":"\u003cp\u003eThe Amora plant containers are the perfect indoor plant containers, sealed to prevent any water leaking on your floor.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThese containers feature a Metal Blue cracked varnish finish.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cu\u003eSizes available\u003c\/u\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"c-product-details__attribute ng-star-inserted\" _ngcontent-angular-nieuwkoop-ssr-c111=\"\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSize 1\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"c-product-details__attribute ng-star-inserted\" _ngcontent-angular-nieuwkoop-ssr-c111=\"\"\u003eHeight: 21cm\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"c-product-details__attribute ng-star-inserted\" _ngcontent-angular-nieuwkoop-ssr-c111=\"\"\u003eDepth: 20cm\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"c-product-details__attribute ng-star-inserted\" _ngcontent-angular-nieuwkoop-ssr-c111=\"\